===================================[ USAGE ]================================

1. Add the following lines to `send.to`:
	
	.so ./trial.3
	.ft CLARENDON
	.ps 24
	
	.FROM:
	Your Name
	Street Address
	Locality, Region
	Country, Postcode
	
	.TO:
	Receiver's name
	Their address
	Etc.
	
	.TO:
	Another receiver's name
	Rinse and repeat

2. Run off a copy:

	$ groff -Tps -C send.to > these-guys.ps

